  "body": "# Better visibility of ores\nTexturepack adds border to every ore and make them easier to find\n## MC 1.17+\n![Ores 1.17+](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/prcbs7PM/images/2b396e21b4c81872ecc6c1404cf36a3d9f7b3ec1.png)\n## MC 1.14 - 1.16 (v2.2)\n![Ores 1.16](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/prcbs7PM/images/5fa16e106c10b7c9b54eee48c1f215896656795b.png)\n\nChanged blocks:\n- Coal Ore / Deepslate Coal Ore\n- Iron Ore / Deepslate Iron Ore\n- Gold Ore / Deepslate Gold Ore\n- Diamond Ore / Deepslate Diamond Ore\n- Redstone Ore / Deepslate Redstone Ore\n- Emerald Ore / Deepslate Emerald Ore\n- Copper Ore / Deepslate Copper Ore\n- Lapis Lazuli Ore / Deepslate Lapis Lazuli Ore\n- Nether Quartz Ore\n- Nether Gold Ore\n- Gilded Blackstone\n- Ancient Debris\n- Budding Amethyst\n\nBetter visibility of ores (v5.0+) supports [Respackopts](https://modrinth.com/mod/respackopts) mod (4.0.0+). You can easily disable every texture separately.\n\nThe resurcepack is also available on [CurseForge](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/better-visibility-of-ores)",
